org.jclouds.abiquo.domain.infrastructure

Class Tier

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jclouds.abiquo.domain.DomainWrapper<com.abiquo.server.core.infrastructure.storage.TierDto>
      • org.jclouds.abiquo.domain.infrastructure.Tier

  • public class Tier
extends DomainWrapper<com.abiquo.server.core.infrastructure.storage.TierDto>
    Adds high level functionality to TierDto. The Tier Resource offers the functionality of managing the logic of QoS volume management. These are only logical levels of QoS and the real QoS (networking speed, volume replication, availability) must be configured manually in the infrastructure.
    Author:
    Ignasi Barrera, Francesc Montserrat
    See Also:
    http://community.abiquo.com/display/ABI20/TierResource
